#: ../../library/network.PPP.rst:5
msgid "class PPP -- create network connections over serial PPP"
msgstr "class PPP -- 通过串口 PPP 创建网络连接"

#: ../../library/network.PPP.rst:7
msgid ""
"This class allows you to create a network connection over a serial port "
"using the PPP protocol."
msgstr "此类允许您通过串口使用 PPP 协议创建网络连接。"

#: ../../library/network.PPP.rst:10
msgid ""
"Currently only the esp32 port has PPP support enabled in the default "
"firmware build. PPP support can be enabled in custom builds of the stm32 "
"and rp2 ports by enabling networking support and setting "
"``MICROPY_PY_NETWORK_PPP_LWIP`` to 1."
msgstr ""
"目前只有 esp32 移植版本在默认固件构建中启用了 PPP 支持。可以在 stm32 和 rp2 移植版本的自定义构建中"
"通过启用网络支持并将 ``MICROPY_PY_NETWORK_PPP_LWIP`` 设置为 1 来启用 PPP 支持。"

