msgid "See `AbstractNIC.ipconfig`."
msgstr "参见 `AbstractNIC.ipconfig`。"

#: ../../library/network.PPP.rst:91
msgid "See `AbstractNIC.ifconfig`."
msgstr "参见 `AbstractNIC.ifconfig`。"

#: ../../library/network.PPP.rst:95
msgid ""
"Poll the underlying stream for data, and pass it up the PPP stack. This "
"is called automatically if the stream is a UART with a RXIDLE interrupt, "
"so it's not usually necessary to call it manually."
msgstr "轮询底层流以获取数据，并将其传递到 PPP 协议栈。如果流是具有 RXIDLE 中断的 UART，则会自动调用此方法，因此通常不需要手动调用。"

